1.00	Revie_Sorey	Revie Sorey	Revie Sorey (born September 10, 1953 in Brooklyn, New York) is a former professional American football player who played offensive lineman for nine seasons for the Chicago Bears. Revie lives with his son Trace in the affluent Chicago suburb of Glen Ellyn. Revie's wife Susan has died from cancer in 2011.	
